DISCLAIMER:

This tool is provided for trail camera image analysis purposes. Results depend on
image quality, lighting, environmental conditions, and other factors beyond the
control of the authors.

The authors make no warranties about the accuracy, reliability, or fitness for
any particular purpose. Users should:

1. Always validate results manually, especially for critical applications
2. Test on a small sample before full-scale processing
3. Not rely solely on automated results for important decisions
4. Understand the limitations of both detection methods
5. Use appropriate thresholds for their specific use case

For applications involving wildlife, conservation, or property security,
professional review is recommended.
